rows.label: tlk4750016601_msg0001
rows.name:
Hi there. If you're looking for passage
to Superbia, you should catch a ship
at Rigitte Harbor.

rows.label: tlk4750016601_msg0002
rows.name:
Ysheva Harbor is for ships to the
Holy See, but those don't go very
often, only once every five days.

rows.label: tlk4750016601_msg0003
rows.name:
I recommend staying a while in
Iyasaki over on the neighboring island.
It's the perfect place to unwind.
